name: C2000 Academy
description:
The C2000 Academy is a great resource for developers to learn about C2000 real-time microcontrollers platform. The Academy delivers easy-to-use training modules that span a wide range of topics for all C2000 devices. Additionally, C2000 Academy provides hands-on lab exercises and a full solution for each lab exercise.
C2000 Academy is applicable to all generation-3 devices- F2807x, F2837xS, F2837xD, F2838xS, F2838xD, F28004x, F28002x, F28003x, F280013x and F280015x
